---

# Chunking

Break complex information into digestible sections.

Prefer

Multiple short sections

over

One long page.

Each section should communicate one idea.

---

# Progressive Disclosure

Reveal information gradually.

Start with the essentials.

Allow users to expand into deeper explanations.

Avoid overwhelming first-time users.

