---

# Empty States

Educational empty states should teach.

Instead of

"No flashcards."

Prefer

"You haven't created any flashcards yet. Reviewing flashcards regularly improves long-term retention."

---

# Error Messages

Errors should educate when possible.

Explain

What happened

â†“

Why

â†“

