Never leave users uncertain.

---

# Reading Experience

Avoid giant paragraphs.

Prefer

Lists

Tables

Cards

Quotes

Highlights

Examples

Break information into manageable units.

---

# Calls to Action

Every educational screen should end with a meaningful next action.

Examples

Practice

Review

Continue Lesson

Generate Quiz

Ask AI

Bookmark

Revise Later

Never leave learning journeys unfinished.

---

# Cursor Instructions

Whenever generating educational content

Optimize for learning.

Optimize for retention.

Optimize for confidence.

Optimize for comprehension.

Never optimize merely for visual appearance.

Every screen should help the learner make measurable progress.